# Copy this to ".env" and fill in your API key(s).
# You can also paste them in Settings -> AI Provider after the app starts.
#
# You only NEED one provider. Defaults: Groq for both chat + STT.
# Set the other as a fallback for when Groq's free tokens run out.

# --- Groq (cloud chat + cloud Whisper STT, free tier) ---
# Get a free key at https://console.groq.com/keys
# ONE key powers both the chat model AND cloud transcription.
GROQ_API_KEY=
# Optional overrides:
# GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile      # or llama-3.1-8b-instant (fastest)

# --- DeepSeek (cloud LLM fallback) ---
# Get a key at https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys
# ~$0.14 per million tokens for deepseek-chat (cents per interview).
#   deepseek-chat     - V3, fast, OpenAI-class. Default.
#   deepseek-reasoner - R1, reasoning model. Slower but stronger.
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=
# Optional overrides:
# DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com/v1
# DEEPSEEK_MODEL=deepseek-chat
